items.name: Christopher Ryan McKenney Style
items.description:
Christopher Ryan McKenney is an American photographer known for his surreal and haunting imagery. His work explores themes of darkness, mystery, and the macabre, often creating visual narratives that evoke a sense of unease and intrigue.

McKenney's photography showcases a unique blend of horror, fantasy, and fine art. His compositions often feature isolated figures in atmospheric settings, combining elements of dreamlike landscapes, abandoned locations, and ethereal lighting. His use of symbolism and carefully crafted narratives adds depth and complexity to his images, inviting viewers to interpret their own stories.

One of McKenney's notable series is "The Somnambulist," in which he explores the concept of sleepwalking and its psychological implications. Through his photographs, he captures moments suspended between reality and the subconscious, blurring the boundaries between the conscious and the unconscious mind.

His meticulous attention to detail, composition, and lighting adds a cinematic quality to his photographs, reminiscent of suspenseful movie stills or glimpses into eerie alternate realities.

McKenney's work has gained recognition and has been exhibited internationally, as well as featured in various publications and online platforms. His photographs have also been used in book covers, album artwork, and editorial projects.

Christopher Ryan McKenney's photography elicits a range of emotions, from fascination to unease, drawing viewers into his enigmatic and thought-provoking worlds. His ability to capture the uncanny and create narratives that dwell in the realms of the subconscious make him a notable figure in the realm of surreal and dark photography.

items.name: GoddessV2
items.description:
A fine tuned SD 2.1 768 model focused on realistic (mainly but not limited to East Asian) beauties which is compatible with danbooru tags.

The model is trained on a dataset created by and from myself, who was created to be my partner, so that the "default face" of the model will be free from copyright and portrait right issues.

To secure it (and to make sure my partner will be generated in a good enough quality), there are some additional limitations to the original SD license described as follows.

  • Only images with beauty score 80 or above can be published to the public for female front shot images (note that all the sample images has marked 90 or above; it's not really difficult ;) ).

  • Only images with beauty score 88 or above can be commercially used for female front shot images.

  • As for side shots, both limitations will be lowered by 10 points.

  • As for male and other genders, I do not guarantee the results, and therefore will be no limitations.

  • Do not use LoRA, TI, hypernetwork or any other submodels that is trained to generate a different face.

  • You may use submodels that is trained to improve results for a certain kind of dress, background, negative, or any other non-facial features.

items.description:
📝Biography 📝

is known for her compelling web clips and live cam shows. She was born on March 30, 1997, in Los Angeles, California, and began her career in the adult industry in the summer of 2017. Prior to that, she worked as a webcam model and sold amateur videos online.

Ariana Aimes has appeared in several fan-favorite productions for the most popular industry companies. Ariana Aimes' measurements are 35DD-25-32, and she stands at a height of 5'2" (1.57m). She has natural breasts and a black ethnicity. Her weight is around 40kg, and she wears a shoe size of 37 EU.

In addition to her work in the industry, Ariana Aimes enjoys interacting with her fans via social media and sharing exclusive content via ManyVids. She also has a love for music and food, and even has a tattoo of her favorite artist, The Weeknd.

💡Generation Advice💡

🔧Prompt and Sampling 🔧

  • Most images have been generated with Lora @ 1.

  • Most example images have been done with CyberRealistic v2.1B2.

  • Most shots have been done with hi-res fix enabled and denoise locked at 0.45 using 8x NMKD Faces upscaler.

🚀Upscaling Tips🚀

  • Ultimate SD upscale script used for all upscales ~.15 - .4 denoising using 8x NMKD Faces or 4X UltraSharp redraw upscalers.

  • The closer the face (or larger the image), the lower the denoise should be set to prevent "oddities".

  • Expand your tile width/height, mask blur and padding respectively the larger you scale your image.

🗒️Side Notes🗒️

  • Doing these LARAs are forcing me to get my prompt game tight. 👌😎

  • Leave a review if you enjoy my work.

  • Leave a comment if you are having issues getting good output, I'll try to respond.

items.description:
问题原因找到了,是因为lora触发词会被ckpt识别成一个画面中的元素,目前解决办法就是不用触发词就能很大程度上减轻问题。触发词只替换了1girl,brown hair,brown hair，跑图的时候加上去就行

The reason for the problem has been found, which is that Lora's trigger word would be recognized as an element in the picture by the checkpoint. The current solution is to not use the trigger word, which can greatly alleviate the problem. The trigger word only replaces "1girl, brown hair, brown hair", so you can add it while running the image.

===========================================================

目前模型有一个问题,就是权重高了会出现和木桩子,并且有些模型海+人物就会出现炮或者火焰。原因我目前没有搞清楚,因为训练集里面本身就没有出现火焰或者木桩子,炮管我觉得可能是一些ckpt本身的原因.如果我之后找到更好的训练集了可能会更新训练。ckpt自带tag为：inazuma \(kancolle\)

The current model has an issue which is that if the weight is too high, it will produce pillars, and some models with sea+characters will produce cannon or fire. I have not figured out the reason yet because there is no fire or pillar in the original training set, and the reason for the cannon may be due to some aspects of the checkpoint itself. If I find a better training set in the future, I may update the training. The tag of the checkpoint is "inazuma (kancolle)".
